<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Sigmund Frankengrüner zu Wildstein</head><p>Der Rat versichert die Freundschaft und bittet um Herausgabe der Waren Nürnberger Bürger, die über Niklas Kleißentaler an den Adressaten gelangt sind.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_100" id="50r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_100_r1l1"><expan>Sıgmund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>frankengrün<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l3">ʒu dem vvıltſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_100_r1l4"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Sıgmud als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / von des geſchefts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ Nıclas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l5"><expan>kleıſſental<ex>er</ex></expan> getan hat / den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>keren</expan> . was Jm der hab 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ʒu Beheım </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l7">
<add><ab facs="#facs_100_line_1576678239908_5219">dıe den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu </ab><ab facs="#facs_100_line_1576678242937_5224">Beheim <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_100_line_1576678245525_5229">ward </ab></add> worden ſey . dıeſelb hab eẅch <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> ſey worden vnd darauf begert ob </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l9">Jr vor vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſıcher ſeyt etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l11">wıſſen ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt eẅch niht ʒe ſchıken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts / Denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l12">von der hab <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>kleıſſental<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>geſchaft</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l14">hat . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch mıt fleıſſ . daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_100_r1l13">vns </ab></add> <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab . her gen <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l15">ſchıket ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dıe fürbas <expan>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ſchaff<ex>en</ex></expan> an dıe ſtett da </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l16">ſıe hin gehört . Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_100" id="50r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Sigmund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Frankengrün<ex>er</ex></expan> zu dem Wiltstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Sigmud, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des geschefts
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz Niclas
                                <expan>Kleissental<ex>er</ex></expan> getan hat, den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu
                        <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>keren</expan>, was im der hab, <add>die den
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu Beheim
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ward</add>, worden sey, dieselb hab
                        ewch <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> sey worden und darauf begert, ob ir
                        vor uns und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sicher seyt etc., das
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und wissen zu disen
                                <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> mit ewch niht ze schiken
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts. Denn von der hab
                                <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> die der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>Kleissental<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex>geschaft</expan> hat, <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir ewch mit fleiss, daz ir <add>uns</add>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab her gen
                            <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> schiket, so
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir die fürbas
                            <expan>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>schaff<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        an die stett, da sie hin gehört; denn wo wir ewch lieb
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
